        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Elena Burger\xe2\x80\x99s excellent
         <em>
          <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxVkMtuxCAMRb9m2DXi4SBmwaKb_kbEw0nQEMgAmSp_XzpZVJXAlnxlX_s403DJ5dR7ro38hqmdO-qE3zVia1jIUbFMwWsmuRIj3InX4JkaFQl1mgviZkLUrRxI9sPG4EwLOb07KOUjWbVwo6QWwDk5cydmsN5aye4KnJQe5svXHD5gcqjxheXMCUnUa2t7vYnPG__q7xVKO0zEiMkM9bC1GfcYXN66tvcf6kdbe7jWIEFzyhm9c8r4CEIOfFAMzB2tGKkwyBwM0ij6tPV5A7ot_N9QUnTKzeYS0tLlx2o2jG-hz5963o4U2jn1ZWxEfxFoF8g3k2nBhKUD9pNpHZ_gDDgo4EpeF3dEwKDXqSDd2efelf5MfwAak4uU" rel="" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
           Is This Public?
          </a>
         </em>
         is literally about a smart young person leaving a hedge fund to get into crypto, like Bezos left a hedge fund to get into the internet in 1994. I just backed
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUEGOhCAQfM1wNNCAwQOHvew3DGDrkFFwoN2Nv19GD5t0upOqVFeqgiNccjntniuxzxrp3NEm_K0rEmFhR8UyxsmKHozUamCTVZMw2rBYx7kgbi6ulsqBbD_8GoOjmNOl4Bw0e1ozC60HPgvP5Tx74wYBgwHA0Gsp9Xz7umOKmAJa_MFy5oRstU-ivT7k1wO-2-Sd4horxdCFvDWARQscBB-AC9BK9h10Rig3oJeaS4ciqK53hr99fT8U3xbo6uErufD6vGDFpkw-l5iWRr-ebsP1IlqSsd3tSJHOEZPzK053SLq7umKPCyYsrcNpdNQakiAUKKPA9Heo1oISquFcsuY85aZK_6Z_KqyADA" rel="" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
