        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Crypto projects and protocols are attracting hundreds of millions of investment dollars at multi-billion dollar valuations, and in most cases, they\xe2\x80\x99re trading more on promise than numbers. It\xe2\x80\x99s easy to compare Ethereum\xe2\x80\x99s market cap to Bank of America\xe2\x80\x99s or JP Morgan\xe2\x80\x99s in chuckling disbelief.
        </p>
